Record Class ConnectionTypeResponse

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.maxmind.geoip2.model.ConnectionTypeResponse
Record Components:
connectionType - The connection type of the IP address.
ipAddress - The IP address that the data in the model is for.
network - The network associated with the record. In particular, this is the largest network where all the fields besides IP address have the same value.
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable
public record ConnectionTypeResponse(ConnectionTypeResponse.ConnectionType connectionType, InetAddress ipAddress, Network network) extends Record implements JsonSerializable
This class provides the GeoIP2 Connection-Type model.
